Get you down stairs.
MISTRESS QUICKLY
Here's a goodly tumult!
I'll forswear keepinghouse, afore I'll be in these tirrits and frights.
So; murder, I warrant now.
Alas, alas! put upyour naked weapons, put up your naked weapons.
