[To the Page]  Pay the musicians, sirrah.
Farewell,hostess; farewell, Doll.
You see, my good wenches,how men of merit are sought after: the undeservermay sleep, when the man of action is called on.
Farewell good wenches: if I be not sent away post,I will see you again ere I go.
DOLL TEARSHEET
I cannot speak; if my heart be not read to burst,--well, sweet Jack, have a care of thyself.
